# Title: Disable Microsoft Defender Firewall via Registry
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2022-01-09
# Level: medium
# Description: Adversaries may disable or modify system firewalls in order to bypass controls limiting network usage
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.defense-impairment, attack.t1686.003
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/registry/registry_set/registry_set_disable_defender_firewall.yml

Details="DWORD (0x00000000)" TargetObject="*\\Services\\SharedAccess\\Parameters\\FirewallPolicy\\*" TargetObject="*\\EnableFirewall"